Q: Given a list of dictionaries, return the dictionary that has the least number of keys.
[
    {"a": 1, "b": 2, "c": 3},
    {"a": 4, "b": 5, "c": 6},
    {"a": 7, "b": 8, "c": 9}
]

A: {"a": 1, "b": 2, "c": 3}

